<center><b>HYPERFAITH</b></center>

## GENRE
Sci-Fi, Crime
     
## SYNOPSIS

2102\. A continent is divided into 9 distinct economic blocs. Political borders have been dissolved, but social ones remain in place. Sector 4 is the hub of underworld dealings, and “digicaps”, drugs targeting biomechanical implants, are turning the inhabitants into mindless droids. Odd jobs agency HEX takes on cases that others won’t. What starts as a few isolated incidents eventually points to a larger conspiracy, one that might have connected everyone from the very start.

### Start Date
2017
### Planned medium of delivery
Visual Novel

## CHARACTERS
### PRIMARY
#### HEX
Ascen: Protagonist, Playable character. An employee of HEX who took Y Lan's place after their untimely death.
Y Lan: Ascen's adoptive older sibling. Died during a high-stakes job with HEX.
Freyja: HEX's accountant and executive assistant. Majority cyborg from an accident in her youth.
Nina: Employee of HEX. Former pop idol sensation who left the industry to find who she truly is.

#### DIGICAP
Viris: Reknowned DJ and underground digicap dealer. Assumed ringleader of digicap distribution.

#### OTHER
Rene: Famous model and heir to top-earning cybernetic enhancement company. Contracts HEX regularly for bodyguard services.


### SECONDARY
#### HEX
Ivy: Part-time employee of HEX and a high school teacher. 
Alondra: Part-time employee of HEX. One of the most senior employees.
Isiah: Employee of HEX. Spends the workday being turned down by Ascen.
Isabel: Employee of HEX. Childhood friends with Isiah. Wishes he would notice her instead of Ascen.
Michel: Employee of HEX. Was in love with Y Lan. Despises Ascen and blames him for their death.
Koshka: Employee of HEX. Former marksman with the Bureau of Surveillance and Intelligence.

#### DIGICAP
Dmitri: Viris's right-hand man. Never to be trusted.
Fizzy: Top girl at Motherboard. Distributes digicaps through the club.

#### OTHER
Yun-seok: Heir to top-earning techno fashion company. Ascen's on again/off again boyfriend/sex parter.
Linnea: Heir to top-earning security technologies company. Knows Freyja, but Freyja doesn't remember her.
Mimikej: Koshka's childhood friend. Grew up in the Abysm with him. Member of the Bureau of Surveillance and Intelligence.

### TERTIARY
#### HEX

#### DIGICAP
Parker: Fizzy's nephew. 
#### OTHER
